sentences: Herobust's I'm Aloud EP peaked at #22 on the Billboard "Top Dance/Electronic Albums" on February 13, 2016.
In February 2017, Herobust released the EP Vertebreaker.
Several months later, a remix EP was released, featuring remixers such as  JSTJR, Protohype, Yultron, 4B, Hydraulix and Willy Joy.
In July 2017, he collaborated with Monxx to release the single "Giant Squiddim".
In August 2017, he released "First Person Shooter" as a single.
In September 2017, he released the single "Debt N ‘Eight".
In December 2017, "Blockbuster" was released as a single by Herobust.
